dmca.title: California Amplifier Agreement on Web Site
dmca.body:
To Whom It May Concern:

It has recently come to our attention that Onecle, Inc, posted one of our
agreements on its web site. CalAmp considers all agreements confidential and
proprietary information. Please remove the agreement from your web site
immediately. If the agreement is not removed promptly, we will be forced to seek
alI available remedies. The agreement is at the following Iink:

http://contracts.onecle.com/ydi/cal-amplifier.lic.2000.08.25.shtml

Should you have any questions, I can be reached at (858) 947-1566.

Sincerely,

CalAmp Solutions, Inc.
Frances Playdon
Division Counsel
